    "pause_predict_sessions table is created automatically on startup via _MIGRATIONS for both fresh and existing DBs",
    "Frontend /pause-predict route renders, plays prefix audio, accepts typed answer, shows reveal with full-sentence playback, and displays a final summary",
    "Home page shows a 'Pause & Predict' card linking to the new page",
