  "title": "Reported Speech Transformation drill (direct → indirect speech)",
  "description": "Add a new focused grammar drill 'Reported Speech' where users transform direct speech sentences into reported/indirect speech (e.g., She said, \"I am tired\" → She said (that) she was tired). This targets tense backshift, pronoun shifts, and time/place adverb changes — common pain points for intermediate learners.\n\n**Backend (app/routers/reported_speech.py, new):**\n- POST /api/reported-speech/session → generate 5 items via LLM. Each item: { id, direct: str, context_hint: str (e.g., 'backshift present→past'), reference: str (canonical reported form), accepted_variants: list[str] (common acceptable alternatives like with/without 'that'), focus_tags: list[str] (e.g., ['backshift','pronoun','time-adverb']) }.\n- POST /api/reported-speech/grade → body { item_id, user_answer }. Normalize whitespace/case/punctuation, compare against reference+variants. If no exact match, call LLM to judge with rubric returning { correct: bool, score: 0-100, feedback: str, diff_highlights: list[{type:'missing'|'wrong'|'extra', text:str}] }. Persist attempts.\n- Register router in app/main.py.\n\n**DAL (app/dal/reported_speech.py, new):**\n- save_attempt(user_id, item_id, direct, reference, user_answer, correct, score, focus_tags) → stores in new table reported_speech_attempts.\n- get_recent_focus_weakness(user_id, limit=20) → returns focus_tags with <70% accuracy for adaptive generation hints.\n\n**Schema (app/database.py):**\nAdd to SCHEMA and to _MIGRATIONS:\n```\nCREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS reported_speech_attempts (\n  id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,\n  user_id TEXT NOT NULL,\n  item_id TEXT NOT NULL,\n  direct TEXT NOT NULL,\n  reference TEXT NOT NULL,\n  user_answer TEXT NOT NULL,\n  correct INTEGER NOT NULL,\n  score INTEGER NOT NULL,\n  focus_tags TEXT,\n  created_at TEXT DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP\n);\n```\nMigration entry (idempotent): the CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS statement itself added to _MIGRATIONS list so existing DBs get the new table.\n\n**Frontend (frontend/src/pages/ReportedSpeech.tsx, new + route in App.tsx):**\n- Card shows the direct-speech prompt with speaker icon (TTS button to hear it), a focus-tag chip (e.g., 'Backshift'), and a textarea for the transformed sentence.\n- Submit → shows inline feedback: green check or red X, score bar, diff highlights (missing tokens underlined, wrong tokens strikethrough), and a 'Reveal reference' toggle.\n- Progress dots for 5 items; final summary shows per-tag accuracy (backshift/pronoun/time-adverb) as small bars and a 'Practice weakest tag' CTA that starts a new session biased to that tag.\n- Add entry card on Home quick-drill grid with icon and short description.\n\nTests: unit test for normalization+variant matching in grader, integration test for /session and /grade happy path.",
